        Frances Willard; 

Joan of Arc;
        The Japanese Girl; Nordica; the Nun; the Indian Woman; the Salvation Army Girl; the
       Maid [as in house servant]; The Fish Wife; Miss Ophelia, Topsy, Eva; Mother Goose. *Pop Chart

